Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.19,0:18:14.25,IN-CH_EP06,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來吧 Shinin’ Stars 這裡就是起點
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.70,0:18:18.83,IN-CH_EP06,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了在哪都能看得到我 Shine on!!
